Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吶 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就很在意來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一直都是這個髮夾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就是不知不覺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.93,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數學的筆記忘帶來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？今天有數學課麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 作業也有的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去取一下 你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 作業也沒寫 沒有也一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：印尼語早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了又來了 麻衣老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是必殺——「不打招呼」麼～？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是大型的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像山一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 就像山一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 實際上不是山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看來不是山哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂的 麻衣你生氣的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我昨天從麻衣的便當那——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了一塊西蘭花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以買來啦 西蘭花！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 吃下去之後就立刻想起來麻衣喜歡吃西蘭花來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後就一直覺得很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是因為西蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜花？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 干的蠢事太多了 根本不知道她為哪件事生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總算是有個大體的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想一直都這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 只能老老實實的道歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了你昨天的主食（漢堡）真抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz24\pos(431,483)\bord1\shad1\c&H2B3786&\3c&H13152B&\4c&H6DCDE6&}買的實惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\bord1\shad1\c&H2B3786&\3c&H13152B&\4c&H6DCDE6&\pos(738,527)}標價打七折
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(777,422)}碎豬肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(860,405)}澳大利亞產
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿了你的兔子對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了你的米飯對不起！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑豆剩下了對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 為什麼那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是昨天白天的事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道是更往前的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在麻衣桌子上的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒菩薩的頭被我折斷了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說就那麼隨意拿出來的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說偷偷地埋到了土裡的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(539,332)}麻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(574,341)}衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(610,353)}抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(648,366)}歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(685,378)}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\frz340\pos(721,390)}☆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是重新考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都收好了放在麻衣的桌子上的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又重新考慮了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在焚燒爐裡面燒了的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 麻衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 聽著音樂呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那確實是察覺不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連那都不知道 就好像在自言自語一樣不停的囉嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險啊 差點變成揭露自己的罪行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後半段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後半段 第一次聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 田中君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 可以佔用你一點時間麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:07:02.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H848484&\pos(411,478)}圍\N棋\N子\N怎\N麼\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.77,0:07:02.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\c&H848484&\pos(311,464)}足\N球\N怎\N麼\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 那個髮型啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得符合風紀的話可不可以 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\frz7.809\pos(406,623)}站前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅鑼燒 吃麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘記有卷子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離數學課還有 5分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒的昨天已經借過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一生的願望！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開不了口…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀媽呀 真是不好意思哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺吧 數學的作業哈 有點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 要是行的話哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微讓俺看看哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 Thanks! 謝謝了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下哈 超快就抄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 遲大發了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:07:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個蠢貨！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上開始你就很吵啊 正雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 遲大發了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊是要被裁員了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好像不是數學的卷子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你喝果汁！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學遲到了 爸爸還被裁員了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊都很嚴重啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該注意的才不是那裡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正雄危險啊！正雄會怎樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪是這個時候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有工夫考慮別人的安危啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷子啊 麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 車站那邊的那個也請你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tha Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 這個 就是這個喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這不是有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點拿出來嘛 麻衣你·真·壞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 把這個瞬殺掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手裡這張卷子 是什麼時候的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想去新奧爾良
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 誰會這一題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤城的課真是處處都難死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業沒寫的話就會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題答錯了就會被訓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有幹勁的傢伙會立刻反映到內部報告裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度的威脅 不會那麼巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是23日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學號是23號的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之條！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請假了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽筋了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼偏偏這個時候手臂抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣的話 會進入他的視野！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先去死角 死角 死…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}啊 怎麼了怎麼了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子 先挪挪椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 誰的手機響了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的來電
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓軸戲麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同學們臉上的笑開了花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭 接下來是布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使出力量 石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 砂糖和牛奶都買到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來沒有忘買的東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}今天雞蛋好便宜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}我也買了不少 真實惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有雞蛋的特價的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 還算趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是再去一趟商店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黑貓先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不能飼養啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有個博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 這隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 隨便帶回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 但是很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛… 確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 不可愛麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要養寵物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要好好照顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你能做到麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是什麼都不做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃廁所什麼的你也必須做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃什麼都不做麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不～給你摸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 那 那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 博士博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了哦 這小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我來摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 唰唰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 博士你好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要來 我也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子兩邊也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右爪唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左爪也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴也唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起尾巴 耳朵後面更唰唰的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 但是摸起來試試的話還是尾巴更…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾巴才沒有唰唰的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡疼麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃名乃名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說話圍巾做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 博士好厲害 不如說好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快給阪本帶上試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓叫阪本的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 箱子上面也寫著呢嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 真省事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說話了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想剛才也摸的太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 一般貓叫的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎都是肚子餓了的情況哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為箱子上寫了個阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太省事了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我就跟你說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都多大了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是按人類的算的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經20歲了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該叫俺阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H522611&\bord0\shad0\pos(574,328)}大\N阪\N腔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 接下來能白吃飯的話就多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要經常記得對年長的人持以敬意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來順便我想說一句 你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要因為我是貓就狂摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說清楚的話 我倒不是討厭被別人摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 貓也是有限度的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他放回原來的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(500,360)\shad1\4c&HF7F4F2&}草\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在等著交房租 還送我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連食物都送我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啦 可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的時候就是要互相說明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼需要的東西不用客氣說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢可不可以 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 不要稍微對你好點你就變天狗模樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}譯註：日語裡用天狗形容自負、驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:45.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(500,400)\bord2\blur10}草\N人\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教 教頭 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤解成什麼了啊 校長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軀幹的部分 開啟看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}譯註：納豆= =
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是贏了的話 請你站前的那個東西就不算數了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盒果汁比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready～ GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 你剛才稍微耍了點賴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實多少有點早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那重新擺好姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready～ GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 大意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低估了對手的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這樣一來熱身也完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 再來一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀呀 這可是相當響啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上通宵了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 但是 身心都熱起來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要動真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了啊 剛才在看別的地方來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 連著大意了三次都被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐 差不多該…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 稍微等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 是是 原來如此原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新手運就到此為止了哦 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 堂堂正正的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斯特！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：刀語中咎錯誤口頭禪的正確版本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.56,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是挺有趣的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掰腕子是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 這個拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以 幫我保管一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有這麼認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我差不多點啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊不好好對待的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是也認真不起來麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 下一次要來真的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要 使出必殺技了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說啊 不過是掰腕子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼這麼燃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何況啊 我連想上廁所都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺著從一開始就好奇怪喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站前的那個和 23盒果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:26.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}朝起きて 齒を磨いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:26.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}早晨睡醒後 起床刷牙來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:29.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}あっという間 午後十時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:29.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不知不覺間 已到晚十點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日もたくさん 笑ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.03,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天也遇到 很多歡樂事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}たくさんときめいたな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}也有非常多 刺激與緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}友たちと バカみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}和閨中密友 像笨蛋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:42.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}騷いでる 時にも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:42.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}大聲吵又鬧 偶爾會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}チラチラって 目が合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.40,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}偶爾瞥向你 四目便相接
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:48.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}偶然だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:48.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}這也不過是 偶然事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:51.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初戀なんて言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:51.54,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}初戀什麼的難以說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キャラじゃないんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}因為我不是這樣的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:22:00.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ねぇ 明日も會えるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:22:00.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}吶 我們明天 也會相見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:03.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}まぶたを 閉じると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:03.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}將我的雙眼 合上了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:07.02,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}キラキラ君だらけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:07.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}腦海中只有 亮晶晶的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:10.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今日も樂しかったね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:10.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}今天的我也 開心又愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:14.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}ああ どうしてだな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:14.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}啊 這又是為何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:18.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fad(100,200)\blur3\fs32}Please come true
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.76,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}うれしいな うれしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}真的好開心 真的好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:25.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}はじめまして 戀ごころ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:25.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}第一次見面 我的愛慕心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:28.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}明日まだ 會えるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:28.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}到明天的話 我們又見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:31.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:31.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}現在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:36.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}夢ですぐ 會えるね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:36.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}在夢中很快 我們會見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:42.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}おやすみなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:42.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\blur3}現在晚安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天手臂抽筋了 卷子沒做出來被罵了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太鬱悶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 最後正雄到底怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:22:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 我知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.45,0:23:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁會再給你買一盒的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納豆激□是裝傻役 是不是想要吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}kinase：激□ 是納豆中的一種功能因子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激□是什麼東西哦 還小夜曲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 下一話的日常是 第四話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H54A6FA&\4c&H54A6FA&}たった今　初めて氣づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H54A6FA&\4c&H54A6FA&}就在剛剛 才第一次注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:01.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀に落ちたのだなー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:01.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是陷入戀情了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H46D6C4&\4c&H46D6C4&}24h キミ☆　キミ☆　キミ☆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.51,0:01:04.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H46D6C4&\4c&H46D6C4&}24h 是你☆  是你☆  是你☆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識せざるをえません！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:05.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子想的全部都是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:08.60,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB198E7&\4c&HB198E7&}なんか　いつもと違う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:08.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HB198E7&\4c&HB198E7&}總覺得 和平時不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:07.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:07.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:11.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HAB5D6D&\4c&HAB5D6D&}キミと　ぎこちない會話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:11.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HAB5D6D&\4c&HAB5D6D&}我與你 慌慌張張的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:10.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:14.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5742BB&\4c&H5742BB&}まさか　いや　片思い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:14.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5742BB&\4c&H5742BB&}難道說 不對 單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:12.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩思い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:12.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩相戀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やばい！　視線合っちゃった！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了！ 跟他的眼睛對上了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:20.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1FD9FB&\4c&H1FD9FB&}なになに！？このドキドキ！？
